reviewText: Memories of the 50's,,,  at the movies...

This new release contains 6 shorts previously released by VCI on their 10 comedy collection, sadly now out of print & expensive. Leon Errol Two-Reeler Comedy Collection MAID TROUBLE is the new title here. This set is a more affordable option if you do not have that old set.
I enjoyed the clean comedy from another era. I grew up seeing this type of comedy between main films at the neiborhood movie theatre.
